---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Remove a friend or cancel an outgoing friend request

Usage: remove [OPTIONS] <USERNAME>

Arguments:
  <USERNAME>
          Exact username with an optional leading @

Options:
      --yes
          Skip only the final default-No confirmation

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

This command follows Venmo's native relationship semantics: it removes an established friend or cancels an outgoing request. It does not decline incoming requests and never retries automatically. Exit code 3 means the friendship outcome must be verified independently.
